### **4. MAIN ENTRY POINT** (index.ts)

The main entry must call `defineChannelPluginEntry`:

```typescript
import { defineChannelPluginEntry } from "openclaw/plugin-sdk/core";
import { pulseboardPlugin } from "./src/channel.js";
import { setPulseboardRuntime } from "./src/runtime.js";

export { pulseboardPlugin } from "./src/channel.js";
export { setPulseboardRuntime } from "./src/runtime.js";

export default defineChannelPluginEntry({
  id: "pulseboard",
  name: "PulseBoard",
  description: "PulseBoard channel plugin",
  plugin: pulseboardPlugin,
  setRuntime: setPulseboardRuntime,
  registerFull: (api) => {
    // Optional: Register tools, HTTP routes, etc. only in full runtime
    // Example: api.registerHttpRoute(...)
  },
});
```

**Key exports:**
- Default: Result of `defineChannelPluginEntry()`
- Named exports: Re-export the channel plugin and runtime setter for external use
- `setRuntime`: Called with `PluginRuntime` to initialize the plugin
- `registerFull`: Called for full-runtime registration (tools, gateways, etc.)

